; Regression test for issue #677: Error building current next branch: no type named 'key_type' in 'class ledger::date_specifier_t' (BZ#677)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/677
; The bug was a compile-time error in date_specifier_t; this test exercises
; date specifier / period functionality to confirm it works correctly at runtime.

2024/01/01 Income
    Income:Salary    $-1000.00
    Assets:Checking

2024/02/01 Income
    Income:Salary    $-1000.00
    Assets:Checking

test bal --period "january 2024"
            $1000.00  Assets:Checking
           $-1000.00  Income:Salary
--------------------
                   0
end test
